*********use of calc()*********

makes the layout responsive acc to window size

link---https://css-tricks.com/a-couple-of-use-cases-for-calc/


margin-->outside border

padding--> inside border

if there comes by default spacing around document give margin and padding to 0px using universal selector.

*{
margin:0px;
padding:0px;
}

******instead of using calc () function we can use box sizing as below:**********
* {
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    }

absolute---means relative to browser window or parent div  and relative means relative to present div.
